Required functionalities:
- search movies (titles in multiple languages)
- flag a film as watched
- add film to watchlist
- rate a film
- add a friend
- see a friend's last watched and watchlist
- show upcoming movies

Optional functionalities:
- TV series
- user points (badges?)
- recommend movie
- color themes
- profile picture
- email notifications
- email verification
- i18n support (eng, de, esp)
- https
- MUCH animation
- dynamic search
- export watchlist
- responsive
